# SINDU-MD 👑️ 🇱🇰 - A Javascript WhatsApp User Bot

🔮 *The main hope of creating this bot is to make WhatsApp work easier and faster.*

<p align="center">  
  <a href="https://telegra.ph/file/798fb30f0ac7e57ce251d.jpg">
    <img alt="SINDU-MD" height="300" src="https://telegra.ph/file/798fb30f0ac7e57ce251d.jpg">
  </a>
</p>  

💡 This bot can **auto reply, download media, edit photos/logos, search info, and more**.  
It is created using **[Baileys](https://github.com/WhiskeySockets/Baileys)**.

